Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.32,0:22:44.25,ED-10-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}生きてゆく力が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.25,0:22:48.64,ED-10-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}その手にあるうちは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.64,0:22:50.53,ED-10-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}笑わせてて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.53,0:22:52.92,ED-10-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}いつも　いつも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.92,0:22:55.37,ED-10-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}歌っていて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.37,0:22:58.65,ED-10-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}ほしいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.65,0:23:04.74,ED-10-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}きっとこの恋は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.74,0:23:09.21,ED-10-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}口に出すこともなく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.21,0:23:13.28,ED-10-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}伝わることもなく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.28,0:23:17.71,ED-10-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}叶うこともなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.71,0:23:21.92,ED-10-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}終わることもないでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.92,0:23:26.37,ED-10-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}ただ小さい小さい光になって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.37,0:23:30.42,ED-10-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}アタシのこの胸の
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.42,0:23:34.52,ED-10-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}温度は下がらないでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.72,0:23:39.00,ED-10-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}欲を言えばきりがないので
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.00,0:23:43.25,ED-10-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}望みは言わないけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.25,0:23:46.25,ED-10-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}きっと今のあたしには
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.25,0:23:51.91,ED-10-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}あなた以上はいないでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.13,0:23:56.01,ED-10-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}生きてゆく力が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.01,0:24:00.45,ED-10-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}その手にあるうちは
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.45,0:24:02.31,ED-10-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}笑わせてて
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.31,0:24:04.66,ED-10-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}いつも　いつも
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.66,0:24:07.13,ED-10-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}側にいて
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.13,0:24:09.22,ED-10-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}ほしいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.32,0:22:44.25,ED-10-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}只要心中還有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.25,0:22:48.64,ED-10-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}生活下去的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.64,0:22:50.53,ED-10-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}陪我歡笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.53,0:22:52.92,ED-10-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}希望你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.92,0:22:55.37,ED-10-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}永遠永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.37,0:22:58.65,ED-10-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}歌唱下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.65,0:23:04.74,ED-10-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}這份戀情恐怕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.74,0:23:09.21,ED-10-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}不會有被訴說的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.21,0:23:13.28,ED-10-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}不會被傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.28,0:23:17.71,ED-10-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}也不會實現
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.71,0:23:21.92,ED-10-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}更不會迎來終結
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.92,0:23:26.37,ED-10-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}而是變成一團小小的光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.37,0:23:30.42,ED-10-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}永遠駐留在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.42,0:23:34.52,ED-10-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}我炙熱的胸膛中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.72,0:23:39.00,ED-10-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}人的欲望總是沒完沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.00,0:23:43.25,ED-10-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}所以就將願望藏在心中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.25,0:23:46.25,ED-10-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}但你一定就是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.25,0:23:51.91,ED-10-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}現在的我最需要的那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.13,0:23:56.01,ED-10-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}只要心中還有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.01,0:24:00.45,ED-10-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}生活下去的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.45,0:24:02.31,ED-10-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}陪我歡笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.31,0:24:04.66,ED-10-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}希望你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.66,0:24:07.13,ED-10-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}永遠永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.13,0:24:09.22,ED-10-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}留在我身邊
